Q_DESC:
You are given two string S1 and S2. Find the maximal length of some prefix of the string S1 which occurs in strings S2 as subsequence.

Input
The first line contains string S1. The second line contains string S2. Both strings consist of lowecase Latin letters.

Output
Output one integer - answer to the question.

Constraints
1 = length of S1, S2 = 10^6
